 Politics &amp; Policy: Report on Los Angeles Police Department Finds Racism, Suggests Changes, Gates's Resignation ---- By David J.
 Nazario Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal 07/10/91 WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A14 LAW AND LEGAL AFFAIRS (LAW) LAW &amp; LEGAL ISSUES, HEARINGS, RULINGS, LEGISLATION (LAW) CALIFORNIA (CA) NORTH AMERICA (NME) PACIFIC RIM (PRM) UNITED STATES (US) LOS ANGELES -- A much-awaited report that paints a distressing picture of brutality and racism in the Los Angeles Police Department, and that calls for the resignation of its chief, could prompt changes in law enforcement nationwide.
